flowRoot.flowPara: HAS MADE US ABANDON OUR VALUES

``Traitors have duped hard-working Englishmen and flung our borders wide open. We have allowed unfavourable people to influence our rich culture. This must stop! It is not too late to take action. If we repent and change the current trajectory of our society, we can conserve the Greatness of the Empire.
